It's Alex Berenson Friday! The intrepid reporter joins Clay and Buck with all the latest on covid. Britain is in far worse shape than it was at this time last year, when no one was vaccinated. The desperate move for a third booster. Fauci pulls a Triple Lindy on natural immunity. Will Biden be handcuffed and taken to The Hague for bombing a family of 10, killing 7 children?
